  <para style="toc3">Ekl</para>
  <para style="mt1">Ekiliziastis</para>
  <para style="mt4">(Solomọn dere ya nʼafọ 977 tupu a mụọ Kraịst)</para>
  <para style="imt">Ihe dị nʼime ya</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ihe dị nʼime ya:</para>
  <para style="im">Ihe e dere nʼakwụkwọ a na-egosi anyị na onye ọbụla kpebiri ibi ndụ nke ịgbakụta Chineke azụ adịghị enwe udo nʼobi ya. E gosiri anyị na inweju akụnụba, na amamihe, na ihe ndị ọzọ niile na-eweta obi ụtọ ezughị inye mmadụ udo nʼobi. Ọ bụ naanị mgbe mmadụ sitere nʼịgbaso ihe ndị a bịakwute Chineke ka ọ ga-enwe obi ụtọ juru eju. Ọrụ dịrị mmadụ, dị ka akwụkwọ a si kọwaa ya, bụ ịtụ egwu Chineke na idebe ihe niile o nyere nʼiwu.</para>
  <para style="iot">Usoro e si dee ya:</para>
  <para style="io1">Enweghị isi nke ndụ mmadụ na-adị <char style="ior"><ref loc="ECC 1:1-11">1:1-11</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Ịdị ndụ abaghị uru <char style="ior"><ref loc="ECC 1:12-2:23">1:12–2:23</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Ndọgbu nʼọrụ na mmegbu <char style="ior"><ref loc="ECC 2:24-4:12">2:24–4:12</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Abaghị uru nke ihe dị iche iche <char style="ior"><ref loc="ECC 4:13-11:10">4:13–11:10</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">Nchịkọta okwu: Tụọ egwu Chineke, debe iwu ya <char style="ior"><ref loc="ECC 12">12</ref></char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="ECC 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Ọ nweghị ihe nwere isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 1:1"/>Okwu onye ozizi, nwa Devid, onye bụ eze na Jerusalem.<verse eid="ECC 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 1:2"/>Ihe efu, ihe niile bụ ihe efu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:2">ka onye ozizi na-ekwu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:2">Ihe na-enweghị isi<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ihe efu <char style="xt"><ref loc="PSA 144:4">Abụ 144:4</ref>.</char></char></note> ka ihe niile bụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:2">Ihe niile bụ nnọọ ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 1:3"/>Olee uru mmadụ na-enweta site na ndọgbu niile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:3">ọ na-adọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ?<verse eid="ECC 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 1:4"/>Otu ọgbọ laa, ọgbọ ọzọ abịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:4">ma ụwa na-adịgide ruo ebighị ebi.<verse eid="ECC 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 1:5"/>Anyanwụ na-awa, na-adakwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:5">ma mee ngwangwa laghachi ebe o si awapụta.<verse eid="ECC 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 1:6"/>Ifufe na-efe gaa na ndịda;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:6">feekwa gburugburu gaa nʼugwu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:6">ọ na-efegharị gburugburu ebe niile;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:6">na-efe na-enweghịkwa nsọtụ.<verse eid="ECC 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 1:7"/>Mmiri dị nʼiyi niile na-asọbanye nʼoke osimiri</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:7">ma oke osimiri ejughị eju.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:7">Emesịakwa, mmiri ndị a na-alọghachi nʼiyi ndị a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:7">malitekwa ịsọkwa na-aga nʼosimiri.<verse eid="ECC 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 1:8"/>Ihe niile nọ na-adọgbu onwe ha nʼọrụ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:8">ọnụ apụghị ịkọ ụdị ike ọgwụgwụ dịnụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:8">Otu ọbụla anyị si lee anya, afọ adịghị eju anya anyị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:8">Afọ adịghịkwa eju ntị anyị ịnụ ihe, na ige ntị.<verse eid="ECC 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 1:9"/>Ihe ọbụla nke dịrịla na mbụ ga-adịkwa ọzọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:9">Ihe ndị mmadụ mere nʼoge gara aga ka a ga-emekwa ọzọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:9">Ọ dịkwaghị ihe ọhụrụ ọbụla dị nʼokpuru anyanwụ.<verse eid="ECC 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 1:10"/>Ọ dị ihe enwere ike ikwu sị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:10">“Lee, ihe a bụ ihe ọhụrụ”?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:10">Ọ bụ ihe dịịrị nʼoge gara aga,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:10">nʼoge ndị garalarị tupu oge anyị.<verse eid="ECC 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 1:11"/>Anaghị echeta ndị mgbe ochie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:11">otu aka ahụ kwa, ọgbọ na-abịa abịa</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 1:11">ndị ga-eso ha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:11">agakwaghị echeta ha.<verse eid="ECC 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amamihe enweghị isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 1:12"/>Mụ onwe m bụ onye nkuzi, bụrịị eze Izrel nʼime Jerusalem. <verse eid="ECC 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 1:13"/>Ekpebiri m, were onwe m nye, iji amamihe nnyochapụta ihe m nwere ike ịmata banyere ihe niile a na-eme nʼime ụwa. Olee ụdị ibu arọ bụ nke a, nke Chineke bokwasịrị ụmụ mmadụ? <verse eid="ECC 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 1:14"/>Enyochaala m ihe niile a na-eme nʼụwa chọpụta na ha enweghị isi. Ọ dị ka mmadụ ịchụgharị ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 1:15"/>Ihe gbagọrọ agbagọ, apụghị ime ya ka ọ dizie.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:15">Ihe na-ezughị ezu, enweghị ike ịgụta ha ọnụ.<verse eid="ECC 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 1:16"/>Echere m nʼime obi m sị, “Lee anya! Aghọọla m onye ukwu, bụrụ onye maara ihe karịa ndị eze niile chịrịla na Jerusalem. Enweela m amamihe nʼebe ọ dị ukwu, babigakwa ụba oke nʼihe ọmụma.” <verse eid="ECC 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 1:17"/>Nʼihi ya, agbalịsiri m ike ịmụta ihe dị iche nʼetiti ihe ọmụma, na ịyị ara na nzuzu. Ma ihe m chọpụtara bụ na ọ baghị uru. Ọ dị ka itufu oge ịchọ ụzọ ijide ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 1:18"/>Nʼihi na mgbe amamihe na-aba ụba, mgbe ahụ ka iwe na ọnụma na-ejupụta,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 1:18">oke ihe ọmụma na-ewetakwa oke ihe mgbu.<verse eid="ECC 1:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="ECC 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Ịgbaso ihe na-enye aṅụrị enweghị isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 2:1"/>Echere m nʼime obi m sị, Ugbu a, aga m eji ihe na-enye obi aṅụrị nwaa gị site otu a chọpụta ihe dị mma, ma nke a bụkwa ihe efu. <verse eid="ECC 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 2:2"/>“Ọchị,” ka m sịrị na “ọ bụ ihe nzuzu. Ikpori ndụ, uru gịnị ka ọ bara?” <verse eid="ECC 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 2:3"/>Echere m nʼobi ụtọ m ga-esite nʼịṅụ mmanya. Agbasokwara m ụzọ ibi ndụ nzuzu ma obi m nọ nnọọ na-edu m site nʼamamihe. Olileanya m bụ na m ga-esi otu a chọta ụzọ kachasị mma ndị mmadụ nwere ike iji bie mkpụmkpụ ndụ ha nʼụwa.<verse eid="ECC 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 2:4"/>Arụpụtara m ọtụtụ ihe dị iche iche, ewuru m ụlọ nye onwe m ma nweekwa ubi vaịnị. <verse eid="ECC 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 2:5"/>Ewuru m ubi a gbara ogige ebe izuike, ma kụọkwa osisi na-amị mkpụrụ dị iche iche nʼime ha, <verse eid="ECC 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 2:6"/>wuore onwe m ọdọ mmiri ebe a ga-esi na-agba ubi m niile mmiri. <verse eid="ECC 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 2:7"/>Agbatara m ndị ohu nwoke na nwanyị, nweekwa ndị ohu ọzọ a mụrụ nʼụlọ m. Enwekwara m ọtụtụ igwe ehi na anụ ụlọ karịa eze niile ndị bu m ụzọ chịa na Jerusalem. <verse eid="ECC 2:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 2:8"/>Achịkọtara m ọlaọcha na ọlaedo nye onwe m, na akụnụba nke ọtụtụ ndị eze na-achị ala ha na-atụtara m. E nwetakwara m nye onwe m ndị ikom na ndị inyom ndị na-abụ abụ. Enwekwara ndị iko nwanyị nʼebe ọ bara ụba. Ihe ụtọ niile ndị na-amasị obi nwa mmadụ. <verse eid="ECC 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 2:9"/>E, aghọrọ m onye dị ukwuu karịa eze niile ndị burula m ụzọ chịa na Jerusalem. Ma nʼime ihe ndị a niile, anya doro m, ihe niile ka m ji amamihe tulee.<verse eid="ECC 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 2:10"/>Ihe ọbụla m chọrọ, ka m na-ewere;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:10">egbochighị m onwe m aṅụrị ọbụla.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:10">Obi m ṅụrịrị ọṅụ site nʼọrụ niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:10">nke a bụkwa oke m ketara na ndọgbu niile m dọgburu onwe m.<verse eid="ECC 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 2:11"/>Mgbe m tulere ihe banyere ihe ndị a niile m tinyetụrụ aka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:11">otu m si dọgbuo onwe m nʼọrụ banyere ha,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:11">mkpebi m bụ na ha niile bụ ihe efu, dịka ịchọ ijide ifufe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:11">Nʼezie, ihe niile bụ ihe efu, ha abakwaghị uru.<verse eid="ECC 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amamihe na nzuzu enweghị isi</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 2:12"/>Atụgharịrị m bido ịmụ ihe banyere amamihe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:12">na ịyị ara na nzuzu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:12">Olee ihe ọzọ nke onye ga-anọchi anya eze ga-eme,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:12">karịa ihe ndị ahụ e merela na mbụ?<verse eid="ECC 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 2:13"/>Achọpụtara m na amamihe dị mma karịa nzuzu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:13">dịka ìhè si dị mma karịa ọchịchịrị.<verse eid="ECC 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 2:14"/>Nʼihi na onye maara ihe na-ahụ ụzọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:14">ma isi kpuru onye nzuzu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:14">Ma achọpụtakwara m</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:14">na otu ihe ndaba na-adabara onye amamihe na onye nzuzu.<verse eid="ECC 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 2:15"/>Agwara m onwe m okwu sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:15">“Dịka onye nzuzu ga-anwụ, otu ahụ kwa ka m ga-anwụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:15">Gịnị bụ uru amamihe m niile bara?”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:15">Ekwuru m nʼobi m sị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:15">“Ihe a bụkwa ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 2:16"/>Nʼihi na onye maara ihe na onye nzuzu bụ ndị a na-agaghị echeta ihe banyere ogologo oge dị nʼihu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 2:16">Nʼụbọchị ndị na-abịa nʼihu, a gaghị echeta ha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 2:16">Onye amamihe na onye nzuzu aghaghị ịnwụ.”<verse eid="ECC 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ndọgbu nʼọrụ abaghị uru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 2:17"/>Ya mere, akpọrọ m ịdị ndụ asị, nʼihi na ọrụ a na-arụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ wutere m. Ihe efu ka ọ bụ; ọ dị ka ịchụgharị ifufe. <verse eid="ECC 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 2:18"/>Ihe niile m gbalịrị ịrụpụta ka m kpọrọ asị, nʼihi na amaara m na emesịa, aga m ahapụrụ ha onye ọzọ na-abịa nʼazụ m. <verse eid="ECC 2:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ECC 2:19"/>Onye maara ma ọ ga-abụ onye maara ihe ma ọ ga-abụkwanụ onye nzuzu? Ma ihe niile m ji amamihe ǹka m na ike m rụpụta nʼokpuru anyanwụ ga-abụ nke ya! Ihe a bụ ihe efu. <verse eid="ECC 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ECC 2:20"/>Ya mere, o wutere m nʼobi na m dọgburu onwe m nʼọrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ. <verse eid="ECC 2:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ECC 2:21"/>Nʼihi na mmadụ nwere ike jiri amamihe, na ihe ọmụma na ǹka dọgbuo onwe ya nʼọrụ, emesịa, ha ahapụrụ onye na-enweghị mgbe ọ rụrụ ọrụ ọbụla ihe ndị ahụ niile. Nke a bụkwa ihe efu, na oke ihe ndakwasị. <verse eid="ECC 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ECC 2:22"/>Gịnị bụ uru mmadụ na-enweta na ndọgbu niile ọ na-adọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ? <verse eid="ECC 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ECC 2:23"/>Nʼihi nʼụbọchị ha niile jupụtara naanị nʼihe mgbu na iru ụjụ, ọ bụladị nʼabalị, obi ha anaghị ezu ike. Ihe ndị a bụkwa ihe efu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2:23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="JOB 5:7">Job 5:7</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 14:1">Job 14:1</ref></char></char></note><verse eid="ECC 2:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ECC 2:24"/>Nʼihi ya, ekpebiri m na ọ dịghị ihe ọzọ ga-abara mmadụ uru karịakwa naanị ịnọdụ ala rie nri, ṅụọkwa ihe ma chọta ojuju afọ nʼọrụ ya. Achọpụtakwara m na ọ bụladị nke a si nʼaka Chineke. <verse eid="ECC 2:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ECC 2:25"/>Ọ dịghị onye pụrụ iri maọbụ ṅụọ ma o siteghị na Chineke? <verse eid="ECC 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ECC 2:26"/>Nʼihi na ndị na-eme ihe na-atọ ya ụtọ, ka Chineke na-enye amamihe na ihe ọmụma, na ọṅụ; ma ọ na-enye onye mmehie ọrụ ịkpakọta na ịchịkọba akụnụba nke ọ ga-enyefe nʼaka onye ahụ ihe ya dị Chineke mma. Nke a bụkwa ihe efu; ịchụso ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 2:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="ECC 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Ihe niile nwere oge</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 3:1"/>Ihe ọbụla nwere oge;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:1">mgbe dịkwara ihe ọbụla a na-eme eme nʼeluigwe.<verse eid="ECC 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 3:2"/>Oge ịmụ nwa na oge ịnwụ anwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:2">oge ịkụ ihe na oge ihopu,<verse eid="ECC 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 3:3"/>oge igbu egbu; na oge ịgwọ ọrịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:3">oge itikpọ na oge iwuzi ewuzi,<verse eid="ECC 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 3:4"/>oge ịkwa akwa, na oge ịchị ọchị,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="ROM 12:15">Rom 12:15</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:4">oge iru ụjụ na oge ite egwu,<verse eid="ECC 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 3:5"/>oge ikposa nkume na oge ịchịkọta nkume,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:5">oge ịbakụ na oge ịkwụsị ịbakụ,<verse eid="ECC 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 3:6"/>oge ịchọ ihe, na oge ntufu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:6">oge ịchịkọba, na oge ichifusi,<verse eid="ECC 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 3:7"/>oge ndọwasị, na oge ndụkọta,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:7">oge ịgba nkịtị, na oge ikwu okwu,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="AMO 5:13">Ems 5:13</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 25:11">Ilu 25:11</ref></char></char></note><verse eid="ECC 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 3:8"/>oge ịhụnanya na oge ịkpọ asị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:8">oge ibu agha, na oge ime udo.<verse eid="ECC 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 3:9"/>Gịnị bụ nnọọ ihe mmadụ na-enweta site na ndọgbu niile nke nʼọrụ niile ọ na-arụ? <verse eid="ECC 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 3:10"/>Ahụla m ibu arọ nke Chineke bokwasịrị ndị mmadụ e kere eke. <verse eid="ECC 3:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 3:11"/>O meela ka ihe niile maa mma nʼoge nke ya. O tinyekwala ebighị ebi nʼime obi ndị mmadụ; ma o nweghị ka mmadụ ghọta ọrụ Chineke site na mmalite ruo nʼọgwụgwụ. <verse eid="ECC 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 3:12"/>Nʼihi ya, ekpebiri m na ihe dịịrị mmadụ ịchọ bụ obi ụtọ na inwe aṅụrị na ndụ ya niile. <verse eid="ECC 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 3:13"/>Ihe ọzọ bụ ka mmadụ rie, ṅụọ, ma nwee afọ ojuju na ndọgbu niile ọ na-adọgbu onwe ya, nʼihi na ha bụ onyinye si nʼaka Chineke. <verse eid="ECC 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 3:14"/>Amaara m na ihe niile Chineke mere na-adịgidekwa. O nweghị ihe apụrụ itinye na ya, o nweghịkwa ihe apụrụ iwepụkwa site na ya. Chineke na-eme nke a ka ndị mmadụ tụọ egwu ya.<verse eid="ECC 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 3:15"/>Ihe ọbụla dị ugbu a, adịlarị na mgbe ochie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:15">ihe ọbụla gaje ịdị dịlarị na mbụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:15">Chineke na-eme ka ihe niile mere na mgbe gara aga megharịakwa ọzọ.<verse eid="ECC 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 3:16"/>Ọzọkwa, achọpụtara m otu ihe nʼokpuru anyanwụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 3:16">na ọnọdụ ezi ikpe naanị mmebi iwu jupụtara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:16">nʼebe e kwesiri inwe ikpe ziri ezi ị ga-achọpụta na ihe ọjọọ dịkwa ya.<verse eid="ECC 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 3:17"/>A gwara m onwe m,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 3:17">“Chineke ga-ekpe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:17">ndị ezi omume na ndị ajọ omume ikpe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 3:17">nʼihi na a ga-enwe oge maka ihe ọbụla a na-eme eme,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 3:17">oge dịkwa maka ikpe ọrụ niile nke mmadụ ikpe.”<verse eid="ECC 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 3:18"/>Echere m nʼobi sị, “Ebe mmadụ nọ, Chineke na-anwale ya, ka mmadụ mata na ha dị ka anụmanụ. <verse eid="ECC 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ECC 3:19"/>Nʼihi na ihe na-eche mmadụ na anụmanụ bụ otu. Ha abụọ na-eku ume, ha abụọ na-anwụkwa anwụ. Ọ dịghị ihe mmadụ ji karịa anụmanụ. Ihe niile bụ ihe efu. <verse eid="ECC 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ECC 3:20"/>Ha niile na-alaghachi nʼotu ebe; ọ bụ nʼaja ka ha si pụta, ebe ahụ kwa ka ha ga-alaghachi. <verse eid="ECC 3:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ECC 3:21"/>Onye pụrụ iguzo gbaa akaebe na mmụọ mmadụ na-ala nʼelu ma nke anụmanụ na-ala nʼaja?”<verse eid="ECC 3:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ECC 3:22"/>Nʼihi ya, ahụrụ m na ọ dịghị ihe ọzọ ụmụ mmadụ kwesiri ime karịakwa inwe ọṅụ nʼọrụ ha, nʼihi na nke ahụ bụ oke ha nʼebe a. Onye ga-eme ka ha bịaghachi hụ ihe ga-eme nʼazụ ha?<verse eid="ECC 3:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="ECC 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Mmegbu, ndọgbu nʼọrụ, na enweghị enyi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 4:1"/>Ọzọ, ahụrụ m mmegbu na obi ilu niile dị nʼokpuru anyanwụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:1">anya mmiri akwa ndị a na-emegbu emegbu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:1">ma ọ dịkwaghị ndị nkasiobi ha nwere,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:1">ma ike dị nʼaka ndị mmegbu a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:1">ma ha enwekwaghị ndị nkasiobi.<verse eid="ECC 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 4:2"/>Nʼihi ya, ekwuru m, na ndị nwụrụ anwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:2">bụ ndị nwụrụ anwụ mgbe gara aga,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:2">ka ndị dị ndụ mma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:2">bụ ndị nke dị ndụ ruo ugbu a.<verse eid="ECC 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 4:3"/>Ma ọ dị mma karịa ha abụọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:3">bụ onye ahụ a na-amụbeghị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:3">onye na-ahụbeghị ihe ọjọọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:3">nke dị nʼokpuru anyanwụ.<verse eid="ECC 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 4:4"/>Achọpụtakwara m na ihe mere ndị mmadụ ji na-adọgbu onwe ha nʼọrụ bụ nʼihi anya ụfụ ha nwere nʼebe ihe ndị agbataobi ha dị. Nke a bụ ihe efu, ịchụso ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 4:5"/>Onye nzuzu na-afanye aka abụọ nʼapata,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:5">na-eri anụ ahụ onwe ya.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="PRO 24:30-31">Ilu 24:30-31</ref></char></char></note><verse eid="ECC 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 4:6"/>Ọ ka mma inwe ihe ntakịrị na obi udo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:6">karịa mmadụ inweju akụ site nʼịdọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:6">nke bụ naanị ịchụso ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 4:7"/>Ọ dịkwa ihe ọzọ m hụrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ bụ naanị ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 4:8"/>Ọ dị otu nwoke nke naanị ya nọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:8">o nweghị nwa, o nwekwaghị ụmụnne.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:8">Mgbe niile, ọ na-adọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:8">ma nke a emeghị ka afọ ju ya nʼakụnụba o nwere.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:8">Ọ jụrụ sị, “Ọ bụ nʼihi onye ka m ji adọgbu onwe m nʼọrụ,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:8">“nʼihi gịnị ka m ji anapụ onwe m ihe obi aṅụrị?”</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:8">Ihe nke a enweghị isi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:8">ihe efu na-eweta obi mgbawa ka ha bụ.<verse eid="ECC 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 4:9"/>Mmadụ abụọ ka mma karịa otu onye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:9">nʼihi na ha ga-arụpụta ọtụtụ ihe:<verse eid="ECC 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 4:10"/>Otu onye nʼime ha daa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:10">onye nke ọzọ ga-apalite ya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:10">Ma mgbe ọ bụ naanị otu onye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:10">onye ga-apalite ya? Ọ nọ nʼime nsogbu.<verse eid="ECC 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 4:11"/>Ọzọ, ọ bụrụ na mmadụ abụọ edinakọ, ahụ ga-ekpokwa ha ọkụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:11">ma olee otu onye naanị ya dina ga-esi nweta okpomọkụ?<verse eid="ECC 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 4:12"/>Ọ bụ ezie na e nwere ike merie onye naanị ya guzo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 4:12">ma mmadụ abụọ pụrụ iguzo zọọ onwe ha.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 4:12">Ụdọ e ji eriri atọ tụkọta nʼotu, adịghị adọbi ya ngwangwa.<verse eid="ECC 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ọganihu enweghị isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 4:13"/>Ọ ka mma ịbụ nwantakịrị na onye ogbenye nwere nghọta karịa ịbụ agadi bụ eze ndị nzuzu, onye na-adịghị aṅa ntị na ndụmọdụ ọbụla. <verse eid="ECC 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 4:14"/>Nwata dị otu a, ma eleghị anya, ọ ga-esi nʼụlọ mkpọrọ pụta bụrụ eze, ma ọ bụkwanụ na a mụrụ ya ogbenye nʼalaeze ahụ. <verse eid="ECC 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 4:15"/>Ahụrụ m na mmadụ niile ndị bi nʼokpuru anyanwụ na-eso nwantakịrị ahụ onye nọchiri anya eze. <verse eid="ECC 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 4:16"/>A pụghị ịgụta ndị dịnyere ya, ma ndị ga-esota nʼazụ agaghị enwe ọṅụ nʼebe onye nọchiri eze ahụ nọ. Ọzọkwa, nke a bụ ihe efu, naanị ịchụso ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 4:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="ECC 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Kwụghachi nkwa ị kwere Chineke</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 5:1"/>Mgbe ị na-aba nʼụlọ ukwu Chineke, lezie anya. Meghee ntị gị nke ọma, karịa ịchụ aja onyinye nke ndị nzuzu, ndị na-amaghị na ha na-eme ihe ọjọọ.<verse eid="ECC 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 5:2"/>Abụla onye na-eme ọsịịsọ ikwu okwu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:2">maọbụ ime ngwangwa nʼime echiche obi gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:2">maọbụ ikwe Chineke nkwa ọnụ efu.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="PRO 20:25">Ilu 20:25</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:2">Nʼihi na Chineke nọ nʼeluigwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:2">ma naanị nʼụwa ka ị nọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:2">nʼihi ya ka okwu ọnụ gị dị ole na ole.<verse eid="ECC 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 5:3"/>Dị ka ọtụtụ nchekasị si eweta ị rọọ nrọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:3">otu a ka okwu onye nzuzu si dị mgbe ọtụtụ okwu dị ya nʼọnụ.<verse eid="ECC 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 5:4"/>Nʼihi ya, mgbe ị na-ekwe Chineke nkwa, atụfula oge imezu ihe ahụ, nʼihi na ihe banyere ndị nzuzu adịghị atọ Chineke ụtọ. Mezuo nkwa niile i kwere Chineke. <verse eid="ECC 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 5:5"/>Ọ ka mma na ị gbara nkịtị karịa na ị ga-ekwe nkwa ma ị gaghị emezu ya. <verse eid="ECC 5:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 5:6"/>Ekwela ka ọnụ gị duba gị na mmehie. Azọkwala onwe gị site nʼịgwa onyeozi Chineke, “na i kwere nkwa a na-amaghị ama.” Nʼihi gịnị ka Chineke ga-eji wee iwe nʼihi ihe ị kwuru, ma bibiekwa ọrụ aka gị? <verse eid="ECC 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 5:7"/>Aga m eme, aga m eme, ma e meghị ya bụ naanị okwu efu. Ya mere, tụọ egwu Chineke.<verse eid="ECC 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Akụnụba enweghị isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 5:8"/>Ọ bụrụ na ị hụ ebe a na-emegbu ndị ogbenye, na-anapụkwa ha ihe ruru ha site nʼikpe ikpe na-ezighị ezi na mpaghara obodo a na-achị achị, ya ejula gị anya, nʼihi na onyeisi ọbụla nwere onye na-atụrụ ya. Ndịisi na-atụ iwu nwekwara ndị kachasị ha elu. Otu a kwa, ọ dịkwa ndị dị elu karịa ha. <verse eid="ECC 5:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 5:9"/>Mgbe ihe nnweta si nʼala ubi bara ụba, ọ na-abara onye ọbụla uru; ọ na-abakwara eze nʼonwe ya uru.<verse eid="ECC 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 5:10"/>Onye ọbụla hụrụ ego nʼanya, ọ gaghị eju ya afọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:10">Onye ọbụla hụrụ akụnụba nʼanya adịghị enwe afọ ojuju nʼihe ọbụla.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:10">Nke a bụkwa ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 5:11"/>Akụ na-abawanye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:11">ndị na-eri ya na-abawanyekwa.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:11">Olee uru ha bara nye onyenwe ha</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:11">karịa iji anya ya abụọ na-ele ha?<verse eid="ECC 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 5:12"/>Onye na-arụsị ọrụ ike na-arahụ ụra nke ọma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:12">ma o riri nri nta ma o rikwaranụ nke dị ukwuu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:12">ma oke iriju afọ onye ọgaranya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:12">anaghị ekwe ya rahụ ụra.<verse eid="ECC 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 5:13"/>Ahụrụ m ihe ọjọọ ọzọ nʼokpuru anyanwụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:13">mmadụ debere akụnụba ruo mgbe o wetara ya ihe mgbu,<verse eid="ECC 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 5:14"/>ma akụnụba ndị ahụ bụ ihe furu site nʼọdachi</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:14">nke bụ na mgbe ha mụtara ụmụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:14">o nwekwaghị ihe fọdụrụ ụmụ ahụ iketa.<verse eid="ECC 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 5:15"/>Dịka mmadụ si gbara ọtọ site nʼafọ nne ya bata nʼụwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:15">otu a ka anyị ga-esi hapụ ya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:15">O nweghị ihe ọ ga-ebu pụọ site na ndọgbu niile</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:15">ọ dọgburu onwe ya nʼọrụ.<verse eid="ECC 5:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 5:16"/>Ma nke a bụ ihe ọjọọ nke na-egbu mgbu nʼobi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 5:16">Mmadụ na-ala dịka o siri bịa.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:16">Gịnị bụ uru ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:16">mgbe ọ na-adọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ nye ifufe?<verse eid="ECC 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 5:17"/>Ụbọchị ndụ ya niile, ọ na-eri ihe nʼọchịchịrị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 5:17">site oke mgbagwoju anya, na nsogbu na iwe.<verse eid="ECC 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 5:18"/>Ma achọpụtara m na ọ bụ ihe dị mma na ihe kwesiri omume, ka nwoke rie ihe ma ṅụọkwa ihe ọṅụṅụ Ka ọ chọtakwa afọ ojuju nʼime ndọgbu niile nke ọrụ ọ ruru nʼokpuru anyanwụ, nʼoge mkpụmkpụ ndụ nke Chineke nyere ya. Nʼihi na nke a bụ oke ya. <verse eid="ECC 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ECC 5:19"/>Ọzọkwa, ọ bụrụ na Chineke enye mmadụ akụnụba na ihe nweta, ma nyekwa ya ike ọ ga-eji kporie ndụ nʼime ihe ndị a, ya nabata nke a dị ka oke ya ma were ọṅụ rụọ ọrụ ya. Ha bụ onyinye si nʼaka Chineke. <verse eid="ECC 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ECC 5:20"/>Ebe ọ bụ na Chineke enyela ya obi ụtọ, ụbọchị ndụ ya ekwesighị iwetara ya oke echiche.<verse eid="ECC 5:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="ECC 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 6:1"/>Ọ dị ihe ọjọọ ọzọ nke m hụrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ, nke na-anyịdo ụmụ mmadụ. <verse eid="ECC 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 6:2"/>Chineke na-enye mmadụ akụnụba, na ihe nnweta, na nsọpụrụ, na-emekwa ka ha nwee ihe niile ha chọrọ, ma ọ dịghị enye ha ike ịnụ ụtọ ha; ma onye ọzọ na-anụ ụtọ ha. Nke a bụ ihe efu, bụrụkwa ihe jọgburu onwe ya.<verse eid="ECC 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 6:3"/>Mmadụ nwere ike mụta narị ụmụ, o nwekwara ike nwee ndụ ogologo ruo agadi, ma ọ bụrụ na o nweghị ike ịnụ ụtọ akụnụba ya, ọ bụrụkwa na o nwetaghị ụdị olili ruru ya, ana m asị, na nwa nwụrụ nʼafọ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">a mụkworo amụkwo</char></note> dị mma karịa ya. <verse eid="ECC 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 6:4"/>Ọbịbịa ya e nweghị isi, nʼọchịchịrị ka ọ na-ala, ọ bụkwa ọchịchịrị ka e kpuchiri aha ya. <verse eid="ECC 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 6:5"/>Ọ bụ ezie na ọ gaghị ahụ ihe anwụ anya, ọ makwaghị ihe ọbụla, o nwere izuike karịa nwoke ahụ. <verse eid="ECC 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 6:6"/>A sịkwarị na o biri ndụ puku afọ, okpukpu abụọ, ma ọ nụghị ụtọ akụnụba ya. Ọ bụghị nʼotu ebe ka ha niile na-ala?<verse eid="ECC 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 6:7"/>Ndọgbu niile mmadụ na-adọgbu onwe ya nʼọrụ bụ ka o rijuo afọ,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="PRO 16:26">Ilu 16:26</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:7">ma o nweghị onye na-enweta ihe na-ezuru ya.<verse eid="ECC 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 6:8"/>Olee ụzọ onye maara ihe si dị mma karịa onye nzuzu?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 6:8">Gịnị bụ uru dịịrị onye ogbenye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:8">na ọ maara otu e si akpa ezi agwa nʼihu ndị dị ndụ?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">6:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">nʼebe ndị ọzọ nọ</char></note><verse eid="ECC 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 6:9"/>Ihe eji anya hụ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:9">ka mma karịa oke ọchịchọ!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 6:9">Nke a bụkwa ihe efu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:9">na ịchụso ifufe.<verse eid="ECC 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 6:10"/>Ihe ọbụla dị ugbu a, ka akpọrọ aha na mgbe gara aga.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:10">Amakwaara ihe mmadụ bụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 6:10">mmadụ ọbụla apụghị ịlụso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:10">onye ka ya ike ọgụ.<verse eid="ECC 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 6:11"/>Okwu na-aba ụba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:11">nghọta na-adị nta.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 6:11">O nwere uru nke a bara?<verse eid="ECC 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 6:12"/>Onye mara ihe dịrị mmadụ mma na ndụ, nʼụbọchị ole na ole nke na-abaghị uru o nwere ịgabiga ndụ a dịka onyinyo? Onye pụrụ ịgwa ya ihe ga-eme nʼokpuru anyanwụ, mgbe ọ nwụsịrị?<verse eid="ECC 6:12"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="ECC 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Amamihe</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 7:1"/>Ezi aha<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="PRO 22:1">Ilu 22:1</ref></char></char></note> ka mma karịa mmanụ isi ụtọ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">mmanụ oke ọnụahịa</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:1">Ụbọchị mmadụ nwụrụ ka ụbọchị a mụrụ ya mma.<verse eid="ECC 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 7:2"/>Ọ kaara gị mma ije nʼebe a na-eru ụjụ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:2">karịa ebe a na-eri na-aṅụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:2">Nʼihi na ọnwụ dịịrị mmadụ ọbụla;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:2">ndị dị ndụ kwesiri iburu nke a nʼobi.<verse eid="ECC 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 7:3"/>Iru ụjụ ka ịchị ọchị mma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:3">ihu gbarụrụ agbarụ na-enyere obi aka<verse eid="ECC 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 7:4"/>Onye maara ihe na-eche echiche banyere ọnwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:4">ma onye nzuzu na-eche naanị banyere ikpori ndụ.<verse eid="ECC 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 7:5"/>Ọ ka mma ige ntị nye mba onye maara ihe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:5">karịa ịṅa ntị nʼabụ ndị na-enweghị uche na-abụ.<verse eid="ECC 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 7:6"/>Ọchị onye nzuzu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:6">dị ka mkpọtụ nke ogwu na-ere ọkụ na-eme nʼokpuru ite.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7:6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mgbe ogwu na-ere ọkụ, na-eme mkpọtụ, na-asụkwa anwụrụ, nke a adịghị eme ka ahụ ndị na anya ọkụ ya nʼoge oyi kporo ọkụ.</char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:6">Ihe a bụkwa ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 7:7"/>Iji anya ike nara mmadụ ihe na-eme ka onye mara ihe ghọọ onye nzuzu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:7">iri ngarị na-emerụ obi mmadụ.<verse eid="ECC 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 7:8"/>Ọgwụgwụ ihe ọbụla dị mma karịa mmalite ya!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:8">Ogologo ntachiobi dị mma karịa mpako!<verse eid="ECC 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 7:9"/>Abụla onye na-ewe iwe ọsịịsọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:9">nʼihi na iwe bụ oke ndị nzuzu.<verse eid="ECC 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 7:10"/>Asịla, “Gịnị mere ụbọchị gara aga ji dị mma karịa ụbọchị ndị a?”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:10">Nʼihi na ọ bụghị amamihe ị jụ ajụjụ dị otu a.<verse eid="ECC 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 7:11"/>Amamihe dịka ihe nketa, bụ ihe dị mma.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:11">Ọ na-abara uru nye ndị na-ahụ anyanwụ anya.<verse eid="ECC 7:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 7:12"/>Amamihe bụ ndo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:12">dịka ego si bụrụkwa ndo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:12">ma ụzọ ihe ọmụma ji dị mma karịa bụ nke a:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:12">Amamihe na-echebe ndụ ndị nwere ya.<verse eid="ECC 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 7:13"/>Chee echiche banyere ihe Chineke na-eme.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:13">Mmadụ ọ pụrụ ime ka ọ dịzie adịzie,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:13">bụ ihe Chineke mere ka ọ gbagọọ agbagọ?<verse eid="ECC 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 7:14"/>Mgbe ihe na-agara gị nke ọma, ṅụrịa ọṅụ, nʼihi ọ dịrị gị mma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:14">ma mgbe mmekpa ahụ batara, mata nke ọma</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:14">na Chineke onye na-enye ọnọdụ ọma</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:14">makwa ihe banyere ọnọdụ ọjọọ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:14">Ya mere, o nweghị onye ọbụla nwere ike ịchọpụta</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:14">ọdịnihu ya.<verse eid="ECC 7:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 7:15"/>Ndụ m nʼụwa a bụ ihe efu, ahụla m ihe abụọ ndị a;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:15">onye ezi omume na-anwụ nʼezi omume ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:15">ma onye na-emebi iwu na-ebi ogologo ndụ na mmebi iwu ya.<verse eid="ECC 7:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 7:16"/>Nʼihi ya, abụbigala onye ezi omume oke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:16">emekwala onwe gị onye mabigara ihe oke.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:16">Gịnị mere i ji achọ igbu onwe gị?<verse eid="ECC 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 7:17"/>Abụbigala onye na-emefe ajọ omume oke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:17">abụkwala onye nzuzu!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:17">Gịnị ka ị ga-eji nwụọ mgbe oge gị na-erubeghị?<verse eid="ECC 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 7:18"/>Ọ dị mma ijide otu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:18">na-esepụghị aka na nke ọzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:18">onye na-atụ egwu Chineke ga-enweta uru nʼime ha abụọ.<verse eid="ECC 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ECC 7:19"/>Amamihe na-eme ka otu onye dị ike</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:19">karịa mmadụ iri na-achị otu obodo.<verse eid="ECC 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ECC 7:20"/>Gbaa ụwa niile gburugburu, ọ dịghị otu onye bụ onye ezi omume,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:20">ọ dịghị onye na-eme ihe ziri ezi nke na-adịghị eme mmehie mgbe ọbụla.<verse eid="ECC 7:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ECC 7:21"/>Egela ntị nʼihe niile ndị mmadụ na-ekwu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:21">ị pụrụ ịnụ nkọcha nke ohu gị na-akọcha gị.<verse eid="ECC 7:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ECC 7:22"/>Gị onwe gị maara</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:22">na ọtụtụ oge, ị na-akọchakwa ndị ọzọ.<verse eid="ECC 7:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ECC 7:23"/>Agbalịsiela m ike inwe nghọta. Ekwuru m sị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:23">“Aga m abụ onye amamihe,”</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:23">ma nke a karịrị m.<verse eid="ECC 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ECC 7:24"/>Amamihe adịghị mfe inweta, ọ dị omimi nke ukwuu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:24">ọ bụ onye pụrụ ịchọpụta ya?<verse eid="ECC 7:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ECC 7:25"/>A tụgharịrị uche m ka m ghọta,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:25">iledo na ịchọpụta amamihe na atụmatụ otu ihe niile si dị</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:25">na ịghọtakwa nzuzu nke dị na ajọ omume</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:25">na ịyị ara nke dị na enweghị uche.<verse eid="ECC 7:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ECC 7:26"/>Achọpụtara m na ọ dị ihe dị ilu karịa ọnwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:26">ihe ahụ bụ nwanyị.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:26">Obi ya dị ka ụgbụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:26">Otu a kwa, aka o ji ejikụ gị dị ka ụdọ igwe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:26">Onye ahụ na-eme ihe na-atọ Chineke ụtọ na-esi nʼaka ya gbapụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:26">ma ndị mmehie ka ọ na-enwude nʼọnya ya.<verse eid="ECC 7:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ECC 7:27"/>“Lee, Ihe a ka m chọpụtara,” ka onye nkuzi kwuru:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:27">“Site nʼịtụkwasị otu ihe nʼelu ibe ya ka m matara isi ihe niile.<verse eid="ECC 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ECC 7:28"/>Mgbe m ka na-achọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:28">ma achọtaghị m,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 7:28">nʼetiti puku mmadụ ndị ikom, achọtara m otu onye aka ya dị ọcha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:28">ma ọ dịghị otu nwanyị m chọtara nʼetiti ha.<verse eid="ECC 7:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ECC 7:29"/>Achọpụtara m naanị nke a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:29">Chineke mere ndị mmadụ ka ha bụrụ ndị ụzọ ha ziri ezi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 7:29">ma ha atụgharịala chọrọ ọtụtụ ihe nchepụta gawa.”<verse eid="ECC 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="ECC 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="ECC 8"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 8:1"/>Onye dị ka onye amamihe?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:1">Onye maara nkọwa ihe?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 8:1">Amamihe na-enyekwa ihu ya ihe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:1">na-emekwa ka mgbarụ nke ihu ya gbanwee.<verse eid="ECC 8:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Rubere eze isi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 8:2"/>Asị m, debe iwu eze, nʼihi iyi ị ṅụrụ nʼihu Chineke.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ọtụtụ oge, ndị ọchịchị na ndịisi obodo na-aṅụ iyi nʼihu ndị ọkaikpe, ndị ụkọchukwu nakwa ọha obodo, na ha ga-abụ ndị kwesiri ntụkwasị obi nʼije ozi ha. Ọ bụ ya ka a na-ekwu nʼebe.</char></note> <verse eid="ECC 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 8:3"/>Emela ngwangwa isi nʼihu eze pụọ. Akwagidela ihe ọjọọ nʼihi na ọ ga-eme ihe masịrị ya. <verse eid="ECC 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 8:4"/>Nʼihi na okwu eze nwere ike ọ dịghị onye pụrụ ịjụ ya, Gịnị ka ị na-eme?<verse eid="ECC 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 8:5"/>Onye na-edebe iwu eze agaghị adaba na nsogbu.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:5">Onye maara ihe na-ama mgbe kwesiri na ụzọ kwesiri ime ihe.<verse eid="ECC 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 8:6"/>Ihe niile nwere oge kwesiri ya, ụzọ e si eme ha dịkwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:6">ọ bụ ezie na nsogbu mmadụ dị ukwuu nʼahụ ya.<verse eid="ECC 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 8:7"/>Ebe ọ bụ na o nweghị onye mara ihe na-aga ime,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:7">onye pụrụ ịgwa ibe ya ihe gaje ime?<verse eid="ECC 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 8:8"/>Ọ dịghị onye nwere ike igbochi mmụọ mmadụ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Maọbụ, </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">ifufe</char></note> mgbe ọ chọrọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:8">Ọ dịghị onye nwere ike igbochi ụbọchị ọnwụ ya.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 8:8">Dịka o si sie ike izighachi mmadụ azụ nʼoge agha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 8:8">otu a ka o si sie ike ajọ omume ịtọghapụ ndị na-eme ihe ọjọọ.<verse eid="ECC 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 8:9"/>Ihe ndị a niile ka m hụrụ, mgbe m na-atụgharị uche banyere ihe niile a na-eme nʼokpuru anyanwụ. Mgbe ụfọdụ, mmadụ na-emegide ibe ya si otu a wetara onwe ya nsogbu. <verse eid="ECC 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 8:10"/>Ọzọkwa, ahụrụ m ebe e liri ndị ajọ omume, ndị na-abata na apụkwa site nʼebe dị nsọ, a na-etokwa ha nʼobodo ebe ha mere ihe ndị a. Nke a bụkwa nnọọ ihe na-enweghị isi; ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 8:11"/>Nʼihi na e nyeghị ntaramahụhụ mmehie mgbe o kwesiri, obi ndị mmadụ na-ejupụta nʼatụmatụ ime mmehie. <verse eid="ECC 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 8:12"/>Onye ajọ omume nwere ike mee narị mmehie bikwaa ogologo ndụ, ma amara m na ọ ga-adịrị ndị na-atụ egwu Chineke mma karịa, bụ ndị na-atụ egwu nʼihu Chineke. <verse eid="ECC 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 8:13"/>Nʼihi na ndị ajọ omume adịghị atụ egwu Chineke, ọ gaghị adịrị ha na mma, ụbọchị ndụ ha agaghị agbatịkwa ogologo dịka onyinyo.<verse eid="ECC 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 8:14"/>Ọ dị ihe ọzọ na-enweghị isi nʼụwa: ndị ezi omume na-anata ntaramahụhụ dịrị ndị na-emebi iwu. Ndị na-emebi iwu na-anata ụgwọ ọrụ ruru ndị ezi omume. Nʼezie, ihe ndị a niile bụ ihe efu, ha enweghị isi. <verse eid="ECC 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 8:15"/>Ya mere, ana m ekwupụta, na ikpori ezi ndụ dị mma, nʼihi na ọ dịghị ihe ka mma nye mmadụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ, karịa iri, na ịṅụ, na inwe obi ụtọ. Mgbe ahụ ọ ga-enwe obi ụtọ nʼọrụ ọ na-arụ nʼụbọchị niile nke Chineke nyere ya nʼokpuru anyanwụ.<verse eid="ECC 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 8:16"/>Mgbe m wepụtara obi m ịchọ amamihe na ịghọta ọrụ mmadụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ nke mere na ọ naghị ehi ụra ehihie na abalị, <verse eid="ECC 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 8:17"/>mgbe ahụ ka m chọpụtara ihe Chineke mere. O nweghị onye pụrụ ịghọta ihe na-aga nʼokpuru anyanwụ. Otu ọbụla mmadụ siri gbalịa o nweghị ike ịchọpụta ihe ọ pụtara. Onye maara ihe pụrụ ị sị na a amatala ya, ma nʼezie ọ maghị ya.<verse eid="ECC 8:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="ECC 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Ihe na-eche mmadụ niile</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 9:1"/>Ihe ndị a niile ka m tulere nke ọma nʼobi m, kpebie na ihe ndị ezi omume na ndị maara ihe na-eme dị nʼaka Chineke, ma ọ dịghị onye maara ihe na-echere ha maọbụ ịhụnanya maọbụ ịkpọ asị. <verse eid="ECC 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 9:2"/>Ihe niile na-adakwasị mmadụ niile nʼotu ụzọ ahụ, ma onye ezi omume ma onye ajọ omume, ezi mmadụ na onye na-abụghị ezi mmadụ, onye dị ọcha na onye na-adịghị ọcha, onye na-achụ aja na onye na-adịghị achụ aja.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:2">Dịka ọ dịrị ezi mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:2">otu a ka ọ dịrị onye mmehie;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:2">dịka ọ dịrị ndị na-aṅụ iyi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:2">otu a kwa ka ọ dị nye ndị na-adịghị aṅụ.<verse eid="ECC 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 9:3"/>Nke a bụkwa ihe ọjọọ na-eme nʼokpuru anyanwụ. Otu ihe ndakwasị dịrị mmadụ niile. Ọzọkwa, obi ụmụ mmadụ jupụtara nʼihe ọjọọ na ịyị ara mgbe ha nọ na ndụ, emesịa ha alakwuru ndị nwụrụ anwụ. <verse eid="ECC 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 9:4"/>Naanị ndị dị ndụ nwere olileanya. Ọ ka mma ịbụ nkịta dị ndụ karịa ịbụ ọdụm nwụrụ anwụ.<verse eid="ECC 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 9:5"/>Nʼihi na ndị dị ndụ maara nke ọma na ha ga-anwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:5">ma ndị nwụrụ anwụ amaghị ihe ọbụla;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:5">ha enwekwaghị ụgwọ ọrụ ọzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:5">nʼihi na ha bụ ndị echefurula echefu.<verse eid="ECC 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 9:6"/>Ịhụnanya ha, na ịkpọ asị ha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:6">na ekworo ha gabigara mgbe ha nwụrụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:6">Ha agaghị enwekwa oke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:6">nʼihe ọbụla na-eme nʼokpuru anyanwụ.<verse eid="ECC 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 9:7"/>Ya mere, gaa nʼihu, jiri ọṅụ rie nri gị, jirikwa ọṅụ ṅụọ ihe ọṅụṅụ nʼihi na ọ bụ ugbu a ka Chineke nabatara ọrụ gị. <verse eid="ECC 9:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 9:8"/>Yiri akwa dị ọcha mgbe niile, tee mmanụ na-esi isi ụtọ nʼisi gị.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ihe e ji maara ndị Juu nʼoge mmemme, maọbụ ụbọchị izuike, bụ iyi akwa ọcha na itekwasị mmanụ nʼisi ha.</char></note> <verse eid="ECC 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 9:9"/>Bie ndụ obi ụtọ, gị na nwunye gị ị hụrụ nʼanya, ụbọchị niile nke ndụ ihe efu gị nke Chineke nyere gị nʼokpuru anyanwụ, nʼihi na nke a bụ oke dịịrị gị na ndụ ndọgbu onwe gị nʼọrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ. <verse eid="ECC 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 9:10"/>Ihe ọbụla ị na-eme, were ike gị niile mee ya, nʼihi na ịrụ ọrụ maọbụ iche echiche, maọbụ ihe ọmụma, maọbụ amamihe adịghị nʼala ndị nwụrụ anwụ. Ebe ahụ kwa ka ị na-aga.<verse eid="ECC 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 9:11"/>Ahụrụ ihe ọzọ nʼokpuru anyanwụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:11">ọ bụghị ndị nwere ụkwụ ọsọ na-agbata ihe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:11">ọ bụkwaghị onye sikarịrị ike na-emeri nʼagha;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:11">ọ bụghị ndị maara ihe ka nri dịrị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:11">ọ bụghị ndị nwere nghọta ka akụnụba dịrị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:11">ọzọkwa, ọ bụghị ndị nka ka amara na-adịrị;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:11">kama ọ bụ mgbe na ihe ndaba na-eme ka ihe ndị a dịrị.<verse eid="ECC 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 9:12"/>Nke ka nke, ọ dịghị mmadụ ọbụla maara mgbe oge ya ga-eru:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:12">Ọ dị ka nnụnụ nke mara nʼọnya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:12">maọbụ azụ e jidere nʼụgbụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 9:12">Dịka ha, ụmụ mmadụ na-adaba nʼọnya nke ihe ọjọọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:12">mgbe ha na-atụghị anya ya.<verse eid="ECC 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amamihe dị mkpa karịa nzuzu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 9:13"/>Ahụkwara m ihe ọzọ nʼokpuru anyanwụ, nke a bụ ụdị amamihe nke metụrụ m nʼobi nʼebe ọ dị ukwuu. <verse eid="ECC 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 9:14"/>Ọ dị obodo nke naanị mmadụ ole na ole bi nʼime ya, ma otu eze dị ike chịịrị ndị agha ya bịa ibuso obodo nta a agha. Ndị agha ya gbara obodo a gburugburu na-achọ ịkwatu mgbidi ya. <verse eid="ECC 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 9:15"/>Ma ọ dị otu onye ogbenye bi nʼobodo nta ahụ, onye maara ihe, ọ zọpụtara obodo ahụ site nʼamamihe ya. Ma o nweghị onye chetara ihe banyere ya. <verse eid="ECC 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 9:16"/>Nke a mere m ji sị, inwe amamihe bara uru karịa ịdị ike, ma ọ bụrụ na onye amamihe ahụ bụ onye ogbenye, a ga-eleda ya anya, a gaghị akpọkwa okwu ya ihe.<verse eid="ECC 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 9:17"/>Okwu nke onye maara ihe na-ekwu na nwayọọ ka a na-anụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:17">karịa iti mkpu nke onye na-achị achị nʼetiti ndị nzuzu.<verse eid="ECC 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 9:18"/>Amamihe ka ihe agha niile mma,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 9:18">ma otu onye mmehie na-ala ọtụtụ ezi ihe nʼiyi.<verse eid="ECC 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="ECC 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="ECC 10"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 10:1"/>Ijiji nwụrụ anwụ ga-eme ka mmanụ isi ụtọ sie isi ọjọọ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:1">Otu a kwa, nzuzu nta pụrụ ime ka amamihe dị ukwuu ghara inwe nsọpụrụ.<verse eid="ECC 10:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 10:2"/>Obi onye maara ihe na-eme ka o mee ihe ziri ezi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:2">ma obi onye nzuzu na-eduba ya na mmehie.<verse eid="ECC 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 10:3"/>Ị ga-ama onye nzuzu site nʼije ụkwụ ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:3">nʼihi na o maghị ihe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:3">Ọ bụladị onye ọbụla na-achọpụta onye nzuzu<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="PRO 13:16">Ilu 13:16</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 18:2">Ilu 18:2</ref></char></char></note> ọsịịsọ.<verse eid="ECC 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 10:4"/>Ọ bụrụ na iwe onye ọchịchị ebilie megide gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:4">ahapụla ọnọdụ gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:4">nʼihi na mmụọ dị nwayọọ ga-eme ka mmehie ukwu dị iche iche dajụọ.<verse eid="ECC 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 10:5"/>Ọ dịkwa ihe ọjọọ ọzọ m hụrụ nʼokpuru anyanwụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:5">dịka njehie nke ndị eze na ndị na-achị achị na-ejehie.<verse eid="ECC 10:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 10:6"/>Ahụrụ m ka ndị nzuzu na-enweta ọkwa dị elu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:6">ma ndị ọgaranya adịghị enweta ọnọdụ ruuru ha.<verse eid="ECC 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 10:7"/>Ahụla m ka ohu na-agba ịnyịnya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:7">ma ụmụ eze ji ụkwụ na-aga dịka ụmụ ohu.<verse eid="ECC 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 10:8"/>Onye gwuru olulu ga-adaba nʼime ya!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:8">Onye na-etida mgbidi ka agwọ ga-atagbu.<verse eid="ECC 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 10:9"/>Onye na-arụ ọrụ nʼebe a na-awa nkume ka nkume ga-adakwasị.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:9">Onye na-awa nkụ nọ nʼize ndụ site na ha.<verse eid="ECC 10:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 10:10"/>Ọ bụrụ na anyụike adịghị nkọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:10">ọ bụrụkwa na-amụghị ihu ya amụ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 10:10">a ga-etinye ike karịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:10">ma ịma eme ihe na-eme ka ihe gazie agazi.<verse eid="ECC 10:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 10:11"/>Ọ bụrụ na agwọ ataa mmadụ tupu e kechie ya ọnụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:11">ọ dịkwaghị uru ọ bara na e kechiri ya ọnụ.<verse eid="ECC 10:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 10:12"/>Okwu onye maara ihe na-ejupụta nʼamara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:12">ma okwu onye nzuzu na-eduba ya nʼịla nʼiyi<verse eid="ECC 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 10:13"/>Nʼihi na mmalite okwu ya bụ nzuzu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:13">ọgwụgwụ okwu ya bụkwa naanị mmebi iwu na ịyị ara.<verse eid="ECC 10:13"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 10:14"/>Onye nzuzu na-ekwu ọtụtụ okwu.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="ECC 10:14"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 10:14">Ma o nweghị onye ma ihe na-aga ime,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:14">onye pụrụ ịgwa ya ihe gaje ime mgbe ọ nwụrụ?<verse eid="ECC 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ECC 10:15"/>Ọrụ nke ndị nzuzu na-agwụ ya ike,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:15">ha makwaghị ụzọ ijeru obodo.<verse eid="ECC 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ECC 10:16"/>Ahụhụ ga-adịrị ala nke eze ya bụ nwantakịrị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:16">nke ndị na-achị achị bụ ndị na-akpọ oriri nʼụtụtụ.<verse eid="ECC 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ECC 10:17"/>Ngọzị na-adịrị ala ahụ nke eze ya bụ onye a na-asọpụrụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:17">nke ụmụ eze ya na-eri ihe mgbe o kwesiri nʼihi inweta ike,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:17">ọ bụghị maka ịṅụbiga mmanya oke.<verse eid="ECC 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ECC 10:18"/>Ọ bụ umengwụ na-eme ka ụlọ hie mmiri;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:18">ọ bụkwa umengwụ na-eme ka elu ụlọ malite ize eze.<verse eid="ECC 10:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ECC 10:19"/>Ịkpọ oriri na-eweta ọnụ ọchị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:19">mmanya na-enye obi ụtọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:19">ma ego bụ ọsịsa nye ihe niile.<verse eid="ECC 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ECC 10:20"/>Akọchala eze, ọ bụladị nʼechiche obi gị<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="EXO 22:28">Ọpụ 22:28</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 23:5">Ọrụ 23:5</ref></char></char></note>;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:20">maọbụ bụọ ọgaranya ọnụ nʼime ụlọ ndina gị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 10:20">nʼihi na anụ ufe nọ nʼelu nwere ike buru okwu gị</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 10:20">nwa nnụnụ nwere nku ga-akọ ihe i kwuru.<verse eid="ECC 10:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="ECC 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Ịgbasapụ aka</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 11:1"/>Gbasapụ aka gị nʼinye onyinye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:1">nʼihi na mgbe ọtụtụ ụbọchị gasịrị ị ga-anata ụgwọ ọrụ gị.<verse eid="ECC 11:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 11:2"/>Kee akụ gị ụzọ asaa maọbụ ụzọ asatọ</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:2">nʼihi na ị maghị ụdị ihe ndaba ọjọọ nwere ike ịbịakwasị gị nʼobodo.<verse eid="ECC 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 11:3"/>Mgbe eluigwe rujiri,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:3">mmiri ga-ezo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:3">mgbe osisi dara, maọbụ nʼugwu maọbụ na ndịda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:3">ebe ahụ ka ọ na-atọgbọ.<verse eid="ECC 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 11:4"/>Onye na-ele ikuku anya agaghị akụ mkpụrụ ọbụla,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:4">onye na-ele igwe ojii anya agaghị ewe ihe ubi.<verse eid="ECC 11:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 11:5"/>Dịka mmadụ na-apụghị ịmata ụzọ ikuku si aga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:5">maọbụ otu ndụ ọhụrụ si ebido nʼime afọ nwanyị dị ime,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:5">otu a ka o si dịrị ma mmadụ apụghị ịghọta ọrụ Chineke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:5">onye mere ihe niile.<verse eid="ECC 11:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 11:6"/>Ghaa mkpụrụ gị nʼụtụtụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:6">esepụkwala aka nʼanyasị,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:6">nʼihi na ị maghị nke ga-eto,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:6">maọbụ nke a maọbụ nke ọzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:6">ha niile nwere ike too nke ọma.<verse eid="ECC 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Cheta Chineke nʼokorobịa gị</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 11:7"/>Ìhè dị ụtọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:7">ọ na-amasịkwa anya ịhụ ìhè anyanwụ.<verse eid="ECC 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 11:8"/>Ọ bụrụ na mmadụ adị ndụ ọtụtụ afọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:8">ya ṅụrịa nʼime ihe niile,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:8">ma ya cheta ụbọchị ọchịchịrị</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:8">ga-adị ọtụtụ.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:8">Ihe niile ndị na-abịa bụ ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 11:9"/>Nwa okorobịa, ọ bụ ihe oke ọṅụ na ị bụ okorobịa.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:9">Ya mere, ka obi gị nye gị ọṅụ nʼụbọchị niile nke okorobịa gị.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="LAM 3:27">Akw 3:27</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:9">Mee ihe niile ị chọrọ ime;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:9">gbasookwa ihe niile nke anya gị na-ahụ.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 11:9">Kama, ghọtakwa nke a,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:9">na ị ghaghị ịza ajụjụ nʼihu Chineke nʼihi ihe niile i mere.<verse eid="ECC 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 11:10"/>Ya mere, wezuga nchegbu site nʼobi,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="2TI 2:22">2Tm 2:22</ref>.</char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:10">wezugakwa nsogbu nke ahụ gị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 11:10">nʼihi na okorobịa na ịdị ike bụ ihe efu.<verse eid="ECC 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="ECC 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="ECC 12"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ECC 12:1"/>Ya mere, cheta Onye kere gị</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:1">mgbe ị ka bụ okorobịa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:1">tupu ụbọchị ọjọọ ndị ahụ abịa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:1">na mgbe afọ aka abịarubeghị</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:1">mgbe ị ga-asị, “Ha anaghị atọkwa m ụtọ.”<verse eid="ECC 12:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ECC 12:2"/>Tupu anyanwụ na ìhè,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:2">ọnwa na kpakpando ga-agba ọchịchịrị,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:2">na nlọghachi igwe ojii mgbe mmiri zosiri.<verse eid="ECC 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ECC 12:3"/>Mgbe ndị na-echebe ụlọ ga-ama jijiji,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:3">mgbe ndị dimkpa nwoke ga-ehulata,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:3">mgbe ndị na-akwọ ihe kwụsịrị maka ha dị ole na ole,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:3">mgbe ndị na-elepụ anya site nʼoghere ga-ebido ịgba ọchịchịrị,<verse eid="ECC 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ECC 12:4"/>mgbe e mechiri ọnụ ụzọ nke pụrụ nʼokporoụzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:4">mgbe olu ịkwọ nri ga-adị ala,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:4">mgbe ụda olu abụ ụmụ nnụnụ ga-akpọte ndị mmadụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:4">ma abụ ha niile na-ala ala,<verse eid="ECC 12:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ECC 12:5"/>mgbe ndị mmadụ ga-atụ egwu ebe dị elu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:5">na ihe egwu nke okporoụzọ,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:5">mgbe osisi alụmọnd ga-ama ifuru</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:5">mgbe ụkpana ga na-adọkpụ onwe ya nʼụzọ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:5">agụụ ihe ọbụla ga-akwụsịkwa.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:5">Mgbe ahụ, ndị mmadụ ga-ala ụlọ ebighị ebi ya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:5">ndị na-akwa akwa ga na-agagharị nʼokporoụzọ niile.<verse eid="ECC 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ECC 12:6"/>E, cheta ya, tupu e gbubie ụdọ ọlaọcha ahụ,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:6">tupu e tiwaa ọkwa ọlaedo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:6">tupu ite adawaa nʼisi iyi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:6">tupu e tijie ụkwụ igwe olulu mmiri.<verse eid="ECC 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ECC 12:7"/>Mgbe ahụ, anụ ahụ anyị ga-alaghachi nʼaja ebe o si pụta;<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="GEN 3:19">Jen 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 34:15">Job 34:15</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 90:3">Abụ 90:3</ref></char></char></note></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:7">mmụọ<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12:7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="xt"><ref loc="ECC 3:21">Ekl 3:21</ref></char></char></note> anyị ga-alaghachikwuru Chineke onye nyere ya.<verse eid="ECC 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ECC 12:8"/>“Ihe efu! Ihe efu!” ka onye ozizi kwuru.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:8">“Ihe niile bụ ihe efu!”<verse eid="ECC 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Nchịkọta okwu niile</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ECC 12:9"/>Ọ bụghị naanị nʼonye ozizi ahụ bụ onye maara ihe, o jegharịrị na-ezi ndị mmadụ ihe ọ maara. Ọ tụgharịrị uche chọpụta ọtụtụ ilu, detuokwa ha nʼusoro. <verse eid="ECC 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ECC 12:10"/>Onye ozizi chọpụtara okwu ndị dabanyere nʼusoro, ihe o depụtara bụ ihe ziri ezi na eziokwu.<verse eid="ECC 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ECC 12:11"/>Okwu ọnụ nke onye maara ihe dị ka ndụdụ e ji achụ ehi. Nchịkọta okwu amamihe ndị a dị ka ǹtu a kumiri nke ọma, nke onye na-azụ atụrụ nyere. <verse eid="ECC 12:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ECC 12:12"/>Ma nwa m nwoke lezie anya, atụkwasịla ihe ọzọ nʼelu ihe ndị a.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ECC 12:12">Akwụkwọ a na-ede ede enweghị ọgwụgwụ, ọtụtụ mmụta na-agwụ ike.<verse eid="ECC 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ECC 12:13"/>Ugbu a anụla ihe ndị a niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:13">ma nụrụ ihe bụ nkwubi okwu:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ECC 12:13">Tụọ egwu Chineke, debekwa iwu ya niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:13">nʼihi na nke a bụ ọrụ niile dịrị mmadụ.<verse eid="ECC 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ECC 12:14"/>Nʼihi na Chineke ga-ekpe ọrụ ọbụla ikpe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:14">ya na ihe nzuzo anyị niile,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ECC 12:14">ma ha dị mma ma ha dị njọ.<verse eid="ECC 12:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ECC 12"/>
</usx>
